title: The Prodigy - Invaders Must Die (Complete Era #1)
description:
This is all the music from The Prodigy's "Invaders Must Die" Era (till 02-24-2009). It includes:

* Invaders Must Die (.FLAC format)
* Invaders Must Die (Bonus DVD)(.ISO format)
* Lost Beats (EP)(.FLAC format)
* Omen (Single/Remixes)(.mp3 format)

In case of new (official) Singles and Remixes being released I'll release a new up to date package.

Further more, I'll be seeding this for a while so be my guest to nitpick the songs you like.

Have Fun!
